msgctxt "StringTable_KLib_Buildings,Build_Conv_WallHole_D"
msgid "Can be used as a connection for conveyor belts. "
msgstr "可用作传送带的连接。"

msgid "Capable of being equipped with different modules.\\r\\nRequires a Mining Head to extract ores, some ores require additional modules. Missing Modules will be indicated with a blue light.\\r\\n\\r\\nNOTE: Node purity and modules affect the miner's 'Mining Efficiency'. This value is multiplied with the base extraction rate of the attached mining head.\\r\\n\\r\\nBase Efficiency per Node Purity:\\r\\nImpure: 50%,\\r\\nNormal: 100%,\\r\\nPure: 200%"
msgstr "能够装备不同的模块。\\r\\n需要采矿头来提取矿石，某些矿石需要额外的模块。缺失的模块将以蓝光指示。\\r\\n\\r\\n注意：节点纯度和模块影响矿工的'采矿效率'。该值与所附采矿头的基础提取率相乘。\\r\\n\\r\\n每个节点纯度的基础效率：\\r\\n不纯：50%%，\\r\\n普通：100%%，\\r\\n纯净：200%%"

msgid "Capable of complex distillation and refining processes.\\r\\nHead Lift: 10 m\\r\\n(Allows fluids to be transported 10 meters upwards.)\\r\\n\\r\\nContains both Conveyor Belt and Pipe inputs and outputs.\\r\\n\\r\\nFluid Output: The first fluid output is at the bottom\\r\\nSolid Output: The first solid output is on the right."
msgstr "能够进行复杂的分馏和精炼过程。\\r\\n扬程：10米\\r\\n（允许流体向上运输10米。）\\r\\n\\r\\n包含传送带和管道输入输出。\\r\\n\\r\\n流体输出：第一个流体输出在底部\\r\\n固体输出：第一个固体输出在右侧。"

msgid "Capable of complex distillation and refining processes.\\r\\nHead Lift: 10 m\\r\\n(Allows fluids to be transported 10 meters upwards.)\\r\\n\\r\\nContains both Conveyor Belt and Pipeline inputs and output ports.\\r\\n\\r\\nFluid Output: The first fluid output port is at the top.\\r\\nSolid Output: The first solid output port is on the right."
msgstr "能够进行复杂的分馏和精炼过程。\\r\\n扬程：10米\\r\\n（允许流体向上运输10米。）\\r\\n\\r\\n包含传送带和管道输入输出端口。\\r\\n\\r\\n流体输出：第一个流体输出端口在顶部。\\r\\n固体输出：第一个固体输出端口在右侧。"

msgid "Capable of producing molten metals by either alloying them or melting solid ingredients.\\r\\nMaximum Temperature: 1500°C\\r\\nHead Lift: 10 m\\r\\n(Allows fluids to be transported 10 meters upwards.)\\r\\n\\r\\nContains 1 Conveyor Belt and 2 Pipe Inputs.\\r\\nOutput Order (facing the outputs):\\r\\nThe right Pipe is the first output."
msgstr "能够通过合金化或熔融固体成分来生产熔融金属。\\r\\n最高温度：1500°Crn扬程：10米\\r\\n（允许流体向上运输10米。）\\r\\n\\r\\n包含1个传送带和2个管道输入。\\r\\n输出顺序（面向输出）：\\r\\n右侧管道是第一个输出。"

msgid "Capable of producing molten metals by either alloying them or melting solid ingredients.\\r\\nMaximum Temperature: 1500°C\\r\\nHead Lift: 10 meters.\\r\\n(Allows fluids to be transported 10 meters upwards.)\\r\\n\\r\\nContains 1 Conveyor Belt and 2 Pipe Inputs.\\r\\nOutput Order (facing thhe outputs):\\r\\nThe right Pipe is the first output."
